Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.10,0:02:00.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頃音！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.60,0:02:02.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.37,0:02:05.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.98,0:02:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有件事我必須要問你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.34,0:02:12.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡惠奈嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.65,0:02:15.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種時候你在說些什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.66,0:02:18.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是很重要的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.94,0:02:19.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.25,0:02:22.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在為剛剛的事生氣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.49,0:02:23.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.19,0:02:26.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是那件事不利於我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.40,0:02:29.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.71,0:02:31.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是對於你來說
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.22,0:02:34.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這方面可能會不太有利
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.39,0:02:35.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後也是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.10,0:02:39.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件事很令我悲傷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.19,0:02:42.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為我失敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.34,0:02:44.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失敗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.90,0:02:49.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定這是最後一次被你這樣看著了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.25,0:02:53.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  必須好好地道別呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.83,0:02:55.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  這到底是怎麼回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.47,0:02:57.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直以來都十分感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.15,0:03:04.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.30,0:03:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頃音！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.91,0:03:11.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頃音走掉了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.00,0:03:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小阿  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.48,0:03:19.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想起學姐告訴我的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.32,0:03:25.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人造人好像被命令去色誘阿九斗大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.90,0:03:29.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我根本不認為阿九斗大人會中招
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.50,0:03:33.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但好像那個人造人失敗的話就會被開除監視員一職
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.26,0:03:36.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為我失敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.20,0:03:43.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在這兒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.68,0:03:45.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸和媽媽呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.47,0:03:49.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在裡面被村裡人灌酒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.73,0:03:50.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.23,0:03:55.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為三輪家的少爺畢竟是未來的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.35,0:03:57.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有阿寬在村子也就安寧了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.15,0:04:00.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  學校裡真的有魔王嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.46,0:04:03.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有個被人稱作魔王的人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.07,0:04:07.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不是那個讓村人害怕的魔王
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.58,0:04:08.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.79,0:04:10.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是哥哥的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.36,0:04:12.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  哥哥好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.83,0:04:15.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然三輪家的兒子是個膽小鬼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.00,0:04:19.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看他那樣  在學校的成績應該也不怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.70,0:04:21.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是如果他不能成為祭司的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.79,0:04:23.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村子的未來也是一片黑暗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.74,0:04:27.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是學校裡有個魔王這傳聞好像很盛行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.67,0:04:30.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣勇者不出現也就說不過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.60,0:04:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三輪好像很相信自己的兒子就是勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.39,0:04:37.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.72,0:04:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡長大的孩子只有他不會游泳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.51,0:04:44.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.66,0:04:46.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  我該回宿舍了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.84,0:04:57.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  有客人找我？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.47,0:05:00.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥你是魔王嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.49,0:05:02.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.55,0:05:04.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是有人這麼稱呼我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.60,0:05:05.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.98,0:05:07.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來這裡幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.79,0:05:09.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你妹妹嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.08,0:05:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.05,0:05:15.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我妹妹給您添麻煩了  真是不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.85,0:05:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請告訴我真相
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.82,0:05:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥不是勇者嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.70,0:05:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.56,0:05:17.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇者？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.77,0:05:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這這這…怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.46,0:05:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥是勇者吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.11,0:05:24.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪子…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.67,0:05:27.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.43,0:05:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他本人也不是這麼期望的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.54,0:05:30.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.57,0:05:33.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.35,0:05:36.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我要騙你…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.06,0:05:37.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你是魔王！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.69,0:05:39.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了我不是魔王…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.52,0:05:40.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.80,0:05:43.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有魔王的話也不會有勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.74,0:05:44.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.03,0:05:48.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的哥哥並沒有想過要成為勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.86,0:05:50.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.46,0:05:52.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪子！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.46,0:06:04.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  你知道你都做了些什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.81,0:06:05.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.14,0:06:08.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我現在才知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.03,0:06:12.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只顧著一味否定自己是魔王
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.15,0:06:13.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而連那孩子的心願也一同…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.90,0:06:15.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否定了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.11,0:06:16.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.05,0:06:21.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是三輪自己也在內心深處期盼成為勇者的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.01,0:06:25.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.99,0:06:27.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪子？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.08,0:06:31.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿寬
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.95,0:06:32.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠奈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.14,0:06:34.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹妹呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.32,0:06:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要找到她才行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.08,0:06:38.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我可是吃了一驚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.36,0:06:40.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿寬居然是勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.66,0:06:43.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咱怎麼可能是勇者…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.95,0:06:46.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說咱因為討厭成為勇者才…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.52,0:06:51.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咱就告訴你  這個傳說是多麼的不靠譜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.49,0:06:54.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡就是傳說中的湖
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.32,0:07:00.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.25,0:07:03.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是傳說也沒什麼好奇怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.55,0:07:10.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這片湖其實是海
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.51,0:07:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.34,0:07:14.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它通過地下的洞穴和海相連
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.82,0:07:17.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空氣進入洞穴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.24,0:07:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此根據潮水的狀況會發出聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.23,0:07:21.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.68,0:07:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  在這洞穴中有座祠堂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.53,0:07:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡有勇者之證
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.52,0:07:27.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇者之證？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.22,0:07:31.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那座祠堂是我祖父建的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.80,0:07:33.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且所謂的勇者之證
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.81,0:07:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是一把插在岩石上的小劍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.47,0:07:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是所謂的只有勇者才能拔出的劍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.93,0:07:42.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣你就明白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.46,0:07:45.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咱的家族擅自編造了傳說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.34,0:07:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.70,0:07:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有人的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.65,0:07:53.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.74,0:07:54.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠奈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.28,0:08:02.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,湖啊  傾聽我的呼喊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.00,0:08:04.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.80,0:08:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼呢…？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.92,0:08:08.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我舔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.49,0:08:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.07,0:08:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全的變態行徑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.28,0:08:16.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了  可憐的魔獸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.03,0:08:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.58,0:08:36.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,復活了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.86,0:08:37.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海參
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.12,0:08:43.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼  你看到了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.01,0:08:48.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.90,0:08:50.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.09,0:08:51.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.46,0:09:04.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我妹妹！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.76,0:09:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然缺乏藝術的事很沒趣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.60,0:09:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但既然被看到了就必須讓她消失
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.74,0:09:10.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然你也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.38,0:09:11.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別開玩笑了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.01,0:09:13.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.89,0:09:14.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.03,0:09:17.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它是吸收Mana的魔獸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.66,0:09:19.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mana便是這個世界的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.48,0:09:21.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此它一旦出現的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.17,0:09:24.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠奈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.63,0:09:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全裸地從背後接近別人真不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.74,0:09:32.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這真是藝術啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.65,0:09:34.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.92,0:09:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是魯莽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.38,0:09:38.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我哥哥可是勇者哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.12,0:09:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一下子就能把你幹掉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.60,0:09:50.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.60,0:09:58.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯啊  站起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.03,0:10:01.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真是魯莽的可以
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.39,0:10:04.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是決定性的狀況沒有改變
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.30,0:10:06.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你太弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.60,0:10:07.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.64,0:10:09.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遺憾的是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.42,0:10:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種人不論被做了多麼不講理的事也不會抱怨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.05,0:10:16.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你連怨恨我的資格都沒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.96,0:10:18.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見鬼去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.20,0:10:21.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.20,0:10:21.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿寬！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.46,0:10:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.58,0:10:30.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.39,0:10:42.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.54,0:10:46.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.69,0:10:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是自己起的名但還是告訴你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.04,0:10:50.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是Mr.X
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.70,0:10:52.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心  肯定是個變態
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.73,0:10:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煩人！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.69,0:10:55.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不懂藝術的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.01,0:10:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藝術？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.90,0:10:57.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.99,0:11:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本以為魔王應該更會理解藝術的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.42,0:11:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙知道我被人稱作魔王
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.94,0:11:06.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從昨天開始就一直在觀察我的就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.50,0:11:07.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小阿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.14,0:11:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會是全裸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.69,0:11:17.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你對惠奈都做了些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.59,0:11:19.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼也沒做
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.37,0:11:23.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是接下來會讓魔王大人你看著她被殺死
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.71,0:11:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛隨手收拾掉的小子還真是無趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.35,0:11:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小子？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.14,0:11:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是阿寬
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.31,0:11:30.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿寬被這個人給…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.09,0:11:33.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…殺了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.37,0:11:34.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.31,0:11:35.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你的熟人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.35,0:11:41.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真是厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.57,0:11:43.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不這樣的話也稱不上藝術了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.70,0:11:47.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小阿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.23,0:11:52.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.29,0:11:53.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小阿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.33,0:11:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  放心  我不會輸給那種貨色的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.73,0:11:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以殺人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.43,0:12:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.85,0:12:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底想怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.29,0:12:06.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很簡單  要你眼睜睜看著村子被那個摧毀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.95,0:12:09.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我只用拖住你就可以了  嗶嘣嘣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.03,0:12:10.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.97,0:12:12.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變態
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.76,0:12:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這便是噪音樂曲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.49,0:12:19.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藝術的最高峰  音樂的完美體現
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.47,0:12:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這變態  吵死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.94,0:12:23.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小阿！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.87,0:12:27.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事  阿九斗的身體已用Mana強化過
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.32,0:12:29.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論受到什麼攻擊都應該沒事才對
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.44,0:12:34.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我是對魔法戰的專家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.06,0:12:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我的噪音
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.14,0:12:36.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噪音？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.83,0:12:40.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  人會被無法預測的聲音擾亂心智
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.18,0:12:45.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說  你只要聽到我的噪音便無法使用魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.68,0:12:54.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\q2}我熱愛我的噪音  也就是說只有我一人能用魔法強化我的身體
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.72,0:12:58.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當我驅使著我的藝術戰鬥之時  就算是魔王也得給我趴下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.45,0:13:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小阿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.45,0:13:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿九斗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.55,0:13:08.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心  我是不會殺了魔王先生的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.48,0:13:12.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他可得背上毀滅這個村莊的罪名
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.40,0:13:16.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  目擊這一切的人就必須得死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.83,0:13:20.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是沒有變強
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.00,0:13:25.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我討厭「力量越大  責任就越大」這種說法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.53,0:13:33.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果  我迄今為止僅僅是用各種理由來逃避責任
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.42,0:13:35.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥是勇者吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.59,0:13:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣溺死嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.07,0:13:42.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我會游泳的話  或許還有轉機
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.53,0:13:44.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便從現在開始也不晚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.65,0:13:47.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便現在開始行動也能改變
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.66,0:13:51.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絢子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.68,0:13:57.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別囉嗦了  你我都不願意死在那傢伙面前吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.93,0:14:01.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別在那自作主張
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.41,0:14:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  能站起來固然是好  不過你有對策了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.97,0:14:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  這主意真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.55,0:14:14.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿九斗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.15,0:14:14.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小阿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.29,0:14:23.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得去保護她們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.23,0:14:27.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便我被稱為魔王
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.00,0:14:29.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也視我為常人的惠奈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.08,0:14:32.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及理解了我的服部同學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.97,0:14:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕不能失去她們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.78,0:14:52.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是當不了勇者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.66,0:14:56.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不對  我已經是勇者了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.22,0:14:59.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是說拔出了這個  我才能成為勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.14,0:15:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經是勇者了  不過還沒有符合這一頭銜的力量而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.85,0:15:12.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在開始  我將獲得這份力量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.59,0:15:15.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認證完成  歡迎歸來  Brave
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.23,0:15:25.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是對魔法戰鬥專用單位D13  請下達啟動命令
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.70,0:15:27.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,默認口令為Brave
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.40,0:15:28.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Brave？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.64,0:15:31.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,口令認證完成  開始傳送單元本體
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.75,0:15:42.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳送完畢  電裝系正常  生命維持裝置正常
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.23,0:15:44.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,選擇外氣循環模式
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.26,0:15:48.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,核融合引擎請通過意念輸入
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.25,0:15:53.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\q2}就是這個了  就是這個了  只要有了這個  就能打敗那個變態
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.67,0:15:54.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有那隻魔獸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.81,0:16:02.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你笑什麼笑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.33,0:16:06.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我總算明白了  你那所謂的噪音
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.64,0:16:08.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不過是你靈魂的吶喊聲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.79,0:16:12.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來  如果我靈魂的吶喊聲能更大的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.57,0:16:15.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我便能毫無阻礙使用魔法了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.02,0:16:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果這樣就能消除噪音  那不是人人都能輕易打倒我了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.83,0:16:21.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？你能控制魔法了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.76,0:16:22.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.87,0:16:28.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躺下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.49,0:16:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很高興你能理解我的藝術
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.99,0:16:39.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我在此的行動還有著一個更大的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.92,0:16:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那便是最大的藝術了  相信你也會喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.28,0:16:45.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更大的目的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.69,0:16:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那便是戰爭  戰爭還是戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.88,0:16:50.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是藝術最終的表現
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.19,0:16:53.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在心中迴響的藝術  全是因戰爭而誕生的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.36,0:16:55.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去的獨裁者有一大半都是極具魅力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.96,0:16:57.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,且理解世上所有藝術的天才
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.70,0:16:59.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是這家譜中的其中一人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.95,0:17:02.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是我  唯獨這一點我絕不退讓
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.56,0:17:06.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你在不知不覺間讓周圍的人犧牲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.27,0:17:10.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如現在你堅持己見的時候  你的女人也為你而犧牲了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.67,0:17:16.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種做法並非藝術啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.74,0:17:22.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不像話  我一不在你就什麼也做不了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.45,0:17:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頃音
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.09,0:17:24.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頃音
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.49,0:17:30.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了就會安心的防災斗篷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.63,0:17:33.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頃音  你回來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.15,0:17:35.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我和他們進行了談判
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.51,0:17:40.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,CIMO 8之一  代號  Mr.X
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.97,0:17:41.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.51,0:17:46.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你現在的行動被視為已超出內閣情報官的管理範圍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.82,0:17:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.96,0:17:51.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我將作為紗伊阿九斗的監視員  讓你失去戰鬥力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.03,0:17:55.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是徒勞的  我不會被那個所影響
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.64,0:18:05.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.02,0:18:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可算回來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.91,0:18:17.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在寒暄之前  得先解決那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.17,0:18:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.37,0:18:26.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.72,0:18:31.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有武器嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.16,0:18:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右手配置有高頻刃  左手有單分子刀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.15,0:18:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背上有六發射線
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.31,0:18:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於選擇請參考連接端口
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.57,0:18:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我大致明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.27,0:18:46.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,射線！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.91,0:18:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好猛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.10,0:18:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸  媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.89,0:18:57.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有對大型敵人的破壞性武器嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.77,0:19:01.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對物兵器有兩種  其中一種為核融合炸彈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.35,0:19:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一種呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.40,0:19:03.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高溫等離子球
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.83,0:19:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就用那個了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.11,0:19:05.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.82,0:19:13.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高溫等離子球  固定立場良好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.52,0:19:17.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次元斷層領域展開  5秒後和目標接觸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.57,0:19:35.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我便是Brave  傳說中的勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.04,0:19:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要保護這個男人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.92,0:19:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我反問你一句  有什麼必要殺他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.31,0:19:53.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是為了守護大家才得到的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.37,0:19:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了保護這個島  必須得消滅他
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.32,0:20:13.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  大哥  雪子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.89,0:20:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.39,0:20:17.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿寬  你…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.50,0:20:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被Brave救了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.23,0:20:22.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.89,0:20:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說  內閣對這次CIMO 8的暴走並不知情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.32,0:20:34.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你以此脅迫情報官？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.28,0:20:37.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情報官在賠罪的同時
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.24,0:20:42.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不得不承認馬科特教會對紗伊阿九斗的監視權
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.98,0:20:45.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼那個色誘計劃也取消了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.92,0:20:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我仍然被下達了這個命令
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.67,0:20:52.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我都知道了  不就沒效果了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.91,0:20:54.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是否誤會了什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.22,0:20:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\q2}由於你對女性關係比較遲鈍  我就想對你進行下性教育而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.13,0:21:00.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.52,0:21:04.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原計劃是讓你與家世顯赫的女生結婚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.99,0:21:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿九斗  請和絢子同學結婚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.79,0:21:08.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.11,0:21:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.52,0:21:13.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為阿九斗喜歡惠奈同學
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.43,0:21:15.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以以為任務失敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.68,0:21:17.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過似乎沒有進展
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.06,0:21:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此  就和絢子同學結婚  入贅她家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.65,0:21:28.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什…麼…結婚！？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.72,0:21:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是幹嘛  於是你打算怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.14,0:21:37.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.64,0:21:39.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說啊  我的感受你就一點不顧及嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.39,0:21:42.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我也頗有感觸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.42,0:21:47.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也真的因為接受了這個命令而難過
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.42,0:21:51.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為  其實我也對你…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.76,0:21:52.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頃音…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.29,0:21:59.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡這種攻略方式啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.12,0:22:00.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你逗我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.88,0:22:04.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個小玩笑而已
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.21,0:23:40.02,next,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(323,325)}你迷戀著她嗎？
